r of Communication</a>. Should you be interested in continuing your studies, you can apply for recognition of prior learning (RPL) upon successful completion of this course.</p> <p>Whether you’re looking to upskill, change roles or challenge yourself in a new discipline, you will graduate a holistic and adaptable communications practitioner well-prepared for the inevitable industry advances, challenges, and opportunities yet to come.</p> </div><a class="sup uppercase" href="#" style="display: block; margin-top: 10px;">Read more</a></section>',
