ration-500 ease-in-out pr-4" id="accordion-2-panel-0" role="region"><div class="pb-5"><p>Learn more about <a href="https://www.deakin.edu.au/study/find-a-course">Deakin courses</a> and <a class="link--external" href="https://www.compared.edu.au/institution/deakin-university/postgraduate" target="_blank">how we compare to other universities<span class="dkn-icon icon-externalLink"></span></a> when it comes to the quality of our teaching and learning.</p></div> </div> </div> </section>',
