ortunities and work-integrated learning ensures you graduate with the skills employers value. At the Deakin Law Clinic, our community legal service, you’ll apply your academic training to real cases. Building your ability to analyse complex legal problems and deliver clear, commercially focused advice in a rapidly evolving legal landscape.</p> <p>*QS World University Rankings by Subject 2025</p> </div><a class="sup uppercase" href="#" style="display: block; margin-top: 10px;">Read more</a></section>',
